org.jbox2d.pooling

Interface IOrderedStack<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E -
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CircleStack

    public interface IOrderedStack<E>
    This stack assumes that when you push 'n' items back, you're pushing back the last 'n' items popped.
    Author:
    Daniel
